snippet.textDisplay: Dear Rosie, it's true that we are so excited in your solo debut. we look forward to it, we talked about it everytime. but keep in mind that we love you so much! we will support you no matter what. we know and understand that you want everything to be perfect not only the song but also the timing. so take your time Rosie! don't pressure yourself and don't worry!we will patiently waiting.  fighting! we are proud of you and trust you so much! Love you, Roseanne🖤
snippet.textOriginal: Dear Rosie, it's true that we are so excited in your solo debut. we look forward to it, we talked about it everytime. but keep in mind that we love you so much! we will support you no matter what. we know and understand that you want everything to be perfect not only the song but also the timing. so take your time Rosie! don't pressure yourself and don't worry!we will patiently waiting.  fighting! we are proud of you and trust you so much! Love you, Roseanne🖤
